=== Diana Jayne Gonzales ===

Email: 
<nowiki>[[http://godiane.net/|Diane]]</nowiki> is an humanitarian open source advocate and developer from Metro Manila, Philippines. She is a Enterprise Java Programmer by day, and works on humanitarian causes on her free time. Her interests include Linux, Free and Open Source Software, Java Programming, Web and Mobile Development, Pattern Recognition, and Japanese Language. For fun, she enjoys traveling, singing, nature trips, among others.
